model.name: dePillis2009 - Mathematical model creation for cancer chemo-immunotherapy

body.pre: This is an updated version of a previous model that described the dynamics of cancer treatment, with descriptions of tumour cell numbers, specific and non-specific immune cells (NK, CD8+ T cells and other lymphocytes) with inclusion of chemo- and immunotherapy. This model incorporates new data to provide an improved and more comprehensive model, with specific emphasis on better descriptions of IL-2 dynamics.
